                        <interp inst="t18410510-1531-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 18.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Prosecutrix.</hi>—
